 okвҶҗtest_config(folder name);z;config;userfile;ns;files;export;getj5;fn;link;here;opts
вҚқ Verify that the system is using configuration according to the spex

 getj5вҶҗ{вҺ•JSONвҚ 'Dialect' 'JSON5'вҠўвҠғвҺ•NGET вҚө}

 SetConfig'' вҚқ Clear user config file
 3 вҺ•NDELETE RetryвҠўfolder
 3 вҺ•MKDIR RetryвҠўfolder
 вҺ•EX name
 zвҶҗLinkCreate name folder
 nsвҶҗвҚҺname
 ns.вҺ•FX'foo' '2+2'
 ns.вҺ•FX'bar' '3+3'
 1 ns.вҺ•STOP'foo'   вҚқ Check that Link.Add will NOT register existing stops
 zвҶҗвҺ•SE.Link.Add nameвҲҳ,ВЁ'.foo' '.bar'
 filesвҶҗ2вҠғВЁвҺ•NPARTSвҠғвҺ•NINFOвҚ 1вҠўfolder,'/*'
 вҺ•SE.Link.Stop'bar' 1  вҚқ Check that Link.Stop will NOT register new stops
 assert'''foo'' ''bar'' вүЎвҚҘ{вҚө[вҚӢвҚө]} files'
 linkвҶҗGetLink name
 assert'0=вүўlink.flagged'

вҚқ --- Link.Configure set user config ---
 SetConfig'' вҚқ Clear user config file
 zвҶҗвҺ•SE.Link.Configure'*' 'watch:ns' 'caseCode:1' 'recordFlags:1' вҚқ Set options
 assert'вҲ§/1вҲҠВЁ''watch: '' ''caseCode: ''вҚ·ВЁвҠӮz'
 configвҶҗgetj5 вҺ•SE.Link.USERCONFIGFILE
 assert'(''caseCode'' ''recordFlags'' ''watch'')вүЎconfig.Settings.вҺ•NL -2'
 assert'вҺ•SE.Link.VersionвүЎconfig.LinkVersion.ID'

вҚқ --- Link.Create ---
вҚқ Test that Link.Create uses the user config
 3 вҺ•NDELETE RetryвҠўfolder
 3 вҺ•MKDIR RetryвҠўfolder
 вҺ•EX name

 zвҶҗLinkCreate name folder
 assert'''ns''вүЎ(GetLink name).watch' вҚқ Check that user config was used
 nsвҶҗвҚҺname
 ns.вҺ•FX'foo' '2+2' вҚқ Little foo
 ns.вҺ•FX'FOO' '3+3' вҚқ Big foo
 1 ns.вҺ•STOP'FOO'   вҚқ Check that Link.Add will register existing stops
 zвҶҗвҺ•SE.Link.Add nameвҲҳ,ВЁ'.foo' '.FOO'
 filesвҶҗ2вҠғВЁвҺ•NPARTSвҠғвҺ•NINFOвҚ 1вҠўfolder,'/*'
 assert'''.linkconfig'' ''foo-0'' ''FOO-7'' вүЎвҚҘ{вҚө[вҚӢвҚө]} files'
 linkвҶҗGetLink name
 assert'(,вҠӮ''FOO'')вүЎlink.flagged'
 assert'(,вҠӮ,1)вүЎlink.flags.Stop'

вҚқ Test setting and clearing Stops
 linkвҶҗGetLink name
 zвҶҗвҺ•SE.Link.Expunge name,'.FOO'           вҚқ Should clear stops
 assert'0=вүўlink.flagged'
 configвҶҗgetj5 folder,'/.linkconfig'
 assert'0=config.вҺ•NC ''SourceFlags'''
 zвҶҗвҺ•SE.Link.Stop(fnвҶҗname,'.foo')(1 2 3) вҚқ Set on foo
 assert'(,1)вүЎвҺ•STOP ''',fn,''''
 assert'(,вҠӮ''foo'')вүЎlink.flagged'
 assert'(,1)вүЎlink.flags[1].Stop'
 configвҶҗgetj5 folder,'/.linkconfig'
 assert'(''caseCode'' ''recordFlags'' ''watch'')вүЎconfig.Settings.вҺ•NL -2'
 assert'''ns'' 1вүЎconfig.Settings.(watch caseCode)' вҚқ Check that settings ended up in the directory config
 assert'1вүЎвүўconfig.SourceFlags'
 assert'(,1)вүЎconfig.SourceFlags[1].Stop'
 assert'''foo''вүЎconfig.SourceFlags[1].Name'
 assert'(name,''.foo 1'')вүЎвҺ•SE.Link.Stop name,''.foo'''  вҚқ This will fail

 zвҶҗвҺ•SE.Link.Stop(name,'.foo')вҚ¬
 assert'вҚ¬вүЎвҺ•STOP ''',name,'.foo'''
 configвҶҗgetj5 folder,'/.linkconfig'
 assert'0=вҺ•NC ''config.SourceFlags'''

 zвҶҗвҺ•SE.Link.Break name
 вҺ•EX name

вҚқ Test that explicit settings override any configuration
 zвҶҗ'(watch:''both'')'LinkCreate name folder
 zвҶҗвҺ•SE.Link.Configure name'fastLoad:1'
 assert'''both''вүЎ(GetLink name).watch' вҚқ Explicit setting overrides config
 configвҶҗgetj5 folder,'/.linkconfig'
 assert'''ns'' 1вүЎconfig.Settings.(watch fastLoad)' вҚқ Directory setting should NOT be changed

 вҚқ Now set up a trace and check that it is restored on re-link
 hereвҶҗвҚ•вҺ•THIS                   вҚқ Do not remove the format or here will not be in scope
 вҺ•CS name                      вҚқ Check that it also works with relative names
 zвҶҗвҺ•SE.UCMD'Link.Trace foo 1' вҚқ Call Trace via UCMD from inside the ns
 вҺ•CS here
 linkвҶҗGetLink name
 assert'(,вҠӮ''foo'')вүЎlink.flagged'
 assert'(,1)вүЎlink.flags[1].Trace'
 assert'(,1)вүЎвҺ•TRACE fn'
 zвҶҗвҺ•SE.Link.Break name

вҚқ /// Make a test which verifies that user config does not pollute
вҚқ a directory which has default settings for someting that user config sets
вҚқ zвҶҗLinkCreate name folder

вҚқ Test that folder config is used if user config says nothing

 zвҶҗвҺ•SE.Link.Configure'*' 'watch:' 'caseCode:' 'recordFlags:' вҚқ Clear user config settings
 assert'вҲ§/1вҲҠВЁ''watch:ns'' ''caseCode:1'' ''recordFlags:1''вҚ·ВЁвҠӮz'
 assert'0=вҺ•NEXISTS вҺ•SE.Link.USERCONFIGFILE' вҚқ No settings

 zвҶҗLinkCreate name folder
 assert'''ns''вүЎ(GetLink name).watch' вҚқ used folder config
 assert'(,1)вүЎвҺ•TRACE name,''.foo'''   вҚқ has that trace been restored?
 zвҶҗ(вҠӮ'foo' '22+22')QNPUT folder,'/foo-0.aplf'
 assert'(,1)вүЎвҺ•TRACE name,''.foo'''   вҚқ has that trace been restored after re-fix?
 zвҶҗвҺ•SE.Link.Break name
 вҺ•EX name

вҚқ /// add test that -ignoreconfig also ignores a valid config

вҚқ Test recovery from unreadable user config file
 (вҠӮ'This is not JSON')вҺ•NPUT вҺ•SE.Link.USERCONFIGFILE 1
 zвҶҗLinkCreate name folder
 assert'1вҲҠ''Invalid configuration file''вҚ·z'

 zвҶҗ'(ignoreconfig:1)'LinkCreate name folder
 assert'''Linked:''вүЎ7вҶ‘z'
 zвҶҗ'(ignoreconfig:1)'вҺ•SE.Link.Break name
 assert'1вҲҠ''-ignoreconfig not allowed''вҚ·z'
 zвҶҗвҺ•SE.Link.Break name
 вҺ•EX name

вҚқ Test that it works if there is no user config file
 3 вҺ•NDELETE userfileвҶҗвҺ•SE.Link.USERCONFIGFILE вҚқ Delete the damaged file
 zвҶҗLinkCreate name folder
 assert'''ns''вүЎ(GetLink name).watch' вҚқ used folder config

вҚқ --- Link.Export ---
вҚқ Start by exporting an actively linked namespace
 exportвҶҗfolder,'-export'
 zвҶҗ'(flatten:0)'вҺ•SE.Link.Export name export         вҚқ flatten is meaningless in the context of Export
 zвҶҗвҺ•SE.Link.Configure export'flatten:1'             вҚқ Test setting option in named file
 assert'1вҲҠ''flatten: ''вҚ·z'                          вҚқ flatten:0 is default so was not stored in config
 configвҶҗgetj5 export,'/.linkconfig'
 assert'1вүЎconfig.Settings.caseCode' вҚқ caseCode should be picked up from re-exported link

 zвҶҗвҺ•SE.Link.Break name
 вҺ•EX name

вҚқ --- Link.Import ---
 SetConfig'' вҚқ Recreate (empty) user config
 вҺ•MKDIR export,'/sub'
 (вҠӮ'goo' '4+4')вҺ•NPUT export,'/sub/goo-0.aplf'       вҚқ Put goo in a sub-folder/namespace
 zвҶҗвҺ•SE.Link.Import name export
 assert'''foo'' ''goo''вүЎ',name,'.вҺ•NL -3' вҚқ Should be 2 functions in there after flattening
 3 вҺ•NDELETE export

вҚқ --- Test non-default typeExtensions (fix for #601)
 3 вҺ•NDELETE folder
 opts.typeExtensionsвҶҗ3 2вҚҙ2 'zzza' 3 'zzzf' 4 'zzzo' 9.1вҠЈoptsвҶҗвҺ•NS''
 zвҶҗopts LinkCreate name folder
 zвҶҗвҺ•SE.Link.Break name
 zвҶҗLinkCreate name folder
 linkвҶҗGetLink name
 assert'(getj5 folder,''/.linkconfig'').Settings.typeExtensionsвүЎвҶ“opts.typeExtensions'
 assert'opts.typeExtensionsвүЎ3 2вҶ‘link.typeExtensions'
 zвҶҗвҺ•SE.Link.Break name
 вҺ•EX name

 CleanUp folder name
 okвҶҗ1
